# ROADMAP — <REPO_FRIENDLY_NAME>

Forward-looking view of the current phase, the next phase, and what's
been deferred. **Sized to the problem** — this is a scan-list for
resuming sessions, not a project management artifact.

Sequenced by phase, not by month. Update in place when a phase closes;
never grow open-ended lists — deferred items belong in the plans/
backlog or `<PREFIX>-TODO.md`.

